WEBVTT

00:00.520 --> 00:02.960
We know we missed the signs with faith.

00:03.120 --> 00:04.622
<i>Previously on Greenleaf...</i>

00:04.656 --> 00:06.072
So that's why you came
all the way over here,

00:06.096 --> 00:08.173
to tell me this in person...
Mac just wins?

00:08.207 --> 00:11.532
No, I actually came to say
you may have one last shot.

00:11.567 --> 00:13.452
<i>- I'll take it.
- Deputy Mayor Leonard.</i>

00:13.487 --> 00:15.213
- Walk with me.
- Skip.

00:15.247 --> 00:16.813
- What?
- I need a job.

00:16.847 --> 00:18.413
I should've brought along a suitcase.

00:18.447 --> 00:20.365
What you call that?

00:20.400 --> 00:21.965
A losing hand.

00:21.998 --> 00:24.025
Ooh!

00:24.233 --> 00:26.096
Is that the church's money
you lost in there tonight?

00:26.120 --> 00:28.679
- Most definitely.
- Excuse me, Michaela?

00:28.714 --> 00:30.092
I'm a pastor at Calvary Fellowship.

00:30.116 --> 00:31.672
- Where Mr. McCready worked?
- That's right.

00:31.696 --> 00:32.603
What do you want to know?

00:32.658 --> 00:35.127
- Kevin is gay.
- What?

00:35.162 --> 00:37.461
- So, are you happy now?
- No.

00:37.495 --> 00:40.383
If you ever need someone
to talk to about whatever...

00:40.707 --> 00:42.433
- Thanks.
- I saw your uncle.

00:42.467 --> 00:43.969
He came and asked me for a job.

00:44.002 --> 00:46.849
- Don't.
- Whoa, easy, easy.

00:46.882 --> 00:49.729
<i>Man, I gotta drive home
tomorrow and drive right past the lake</i>

00:49.762 --> 00:51.114
<i>where my little sister drowned herself</i>

00:51.138 --> 00:52.769
<i>because of what that man did to her.</i>

00:52.802 --> 00:54.081
<i>You give him a job,</i>

00:54.114 --> 00:56.096
I'll take your ass apart
six ways to Sunday.

00:56.130 --> 00:58.688
- Who are those from?
- Probably Darlene and Vida.

00:58.722 --> 01:00.864
She had mentioned that they would...
What?

01:00.898 --> 01:04.224
- You stay with the family.
- Wait, where are you going?

01:12.737 --> 01:14.271
<i>He did it again.</i>

01:14.306 --> 01:16.864
Honestly, Gigi, I don't think
he ever really stopped.

01:21.666 --> 01:23.551
<i>Then he put his hands down my pants.</i>

01:23.586 --> 01:24.800
<i>I told him I'd tell.</i>

01:24.833 --> 01:26.304
<i>He said no one would believe me.</i>

