01:53.409 --> 01:55.967
<i>Amen.</i>

01:59.264 --> 02:00.671
<i>Amen.</i>

02:08.672 --> 02:09.982
<i>Well.</i>

02:21.504 --> 02:24.094
<i>Amen, amen.</i>

